Fonner Park, Grand Island, NE, USA

Latitude and longitude coordinates are: 40.902050, -98.328606.

Fonner Park is a small public park Grand Island, Nebraska. It is located in the southeast of the city and is one of the most favorite recreation spot of the local population. It is located near famous Eihusen Arena and sometimes the park is also becoming a venue for various sports related events and celebrations.
